functions.name: Get holders of a membership NFT
functions.description: Returns all Members of a specific Rep3 community

args.name: contract
args.description: A Rep3 community e.g. 0x4fc27be45d5ca34f33c52f420d23c29b72352992 for CULT governance

args.name: level
args.example: 1, 2, 3,...256, all. Level 0 denotes inactive membership. Write `all` for all levels except 0
args.description: A Rep3 level. Level 0 denotes inactive membership. Leave this field empty to query all levels greater than 1. Otherwise, insert a level
